2. ğŸ“¢ Notify all users via all channels
3. ğŸ”§ Deploy fix to testnet
4. ğŸ§ª Test thoroughly
5. ğŸ“ Prepare upgrade/migration plan
6. âœ… Execute with multisig approval

**Upgrade Process:**
```bash
# If using upgradeable contracts (OpenZeppelin)
